<h3>Contents - Part Three</h3>

ii  Summary<br>
<a href="EOC3-summary.html">Biological Invasion as a Global 
Change</a><br>
Peter Vitousek<br>
Lloyd Loop<br>
Carla D'Antonio<p>

1  <a href="EOC3-1.html">Ecosystem Management and Legal 
Strategies to Maintain Ecosystem Integrity</a><br>
