http://gcrio.gcrio.org:80/ASPEN/science/eoc94/EOC1/EOC1-3.html 198.76.82.10 19970101085153 text/html 4865
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
Date: Wed, 01 Jan 1997 08:52:02 GMT
Server: NCSA/1.5.2
Last-modified: Thu, 09 Nov 1995 20:29:32 GMT
Content-type: text/html
