http://gcrio.gcrio.org:80/ASPEN/science/eoc94/EOC1/EOC1-10.html 198.76.82.10 19970101085353 text/html 4484
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
Date: Wed, 01 Jan 1997 08:54:01 GMT
Server: NCSA/1.5.2
