<head>
<title>AGCI Science Program</title>
</head>
<body>
<h2>Science Program</h2>

<a href=eoc.html>Elements of Change</a> is the report of our Summer 
Science Sessions.  You 
will find the complete text of Elements of Change 1994, which deals with
Climate-Radiation Feedbacks: The Current State of the Science, Anticipating
Global Change Surprises, and Biological Invasion as a Global Change.  The
1995 report will be available in January 1996.<p>

<!a href=science95.html><b>1995 Science Program</b><!/a> -  Here you will find descriptions of the themes of our
summer science sessions.  The 1995 sessions were Changes in Global
Vegetative Patterns and Their Relationships to Human Activity, Improving
the Effectiveness of the Climate Convention, and The Metro-Agro-Plex as a
Geographical Unit of Analysis for Regional and Global Environmental Change.
</body>
