<tr><td>MODIS</td><td>Moderate Resolution Imaging Spectrometer 
</td></tr>
<tr><td>MSFC</td><td>Marshall Space Flight Center</td></tr>
<tr><td>NAL</td><td>National Agricultural Library </td></tr>
<tr><td>NALC</td><td>North American Landscape 
Characterization</td></tr>
<tr><td>NARA</td><td>National Archive and Records 
