"Food Security, Population, and Environment" by P. R. Ehrlich,  A. 
Ehrlich, 
and G. C. Daily, <i>Population and Development Review </i>vol 19, pp 
1-32, 
1993. <p>

"How Many People Can the Earth Feed?" by V. Smil. <i>Population and 
Development Review  </i>vol 20, pp 255-292, 1994.<p>

<i>Hunger and Public Action </i> by J. Dr&#232;ze,  and A. Sen. 
Oxford, 
Clarendon Press, 1989.<p>

"Potential Impacts of Climate Change on Agriculture and World Food 
Supply," by C.  Rosenzweig, and D.Hillel. <i>Consequences  </i> vol 1 no 
2, 
pp 23-32, 1995.<p>

<i>Poverty and Famines: An Essay on Entitlement and Deprivation.  
</i>by 
A. Sen. Oxford, Clarendon Press, 1982.<p>

