<TITLE>INNOVATIONS- April 96</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR=#E6E8FA>

<CENTER>
<IMG ALT="INNOVATIONS" SRC="../images/CIT.innovations.interl.gif"><BR>
<B>April 1996</B>
</CENTER>

<UL>
<LI><B><A HREF="./article1.html">Richmond Roundup</A></B><P>
<LI><B><A HREF="./article2.html">Dynamic Engineering Expands</A></B><P>
