<LI><B><A HREF="./article10.html">CIT and Virginia Business Magazine Create Business Intellectual Resource Guide</A></B><P>
</UL>
<P>
<CITE>
INNOVATIONS is published quarterly by Virginia's Center for Innovative Technology (CIT). Building upon its strength in fostering partnerships between Virginia businesses and higher education, CIT strives to enhance the Commonwealth's competitiveness by providing business with access to the state's technology resources and assist in the creation and retention of technology-based jobs and businesses. Direct questions about this newsletter to Debbie Barrigan, Virginia's Center for Innovative Technology, 2214 Rock Hill Road, Suite 600, Herndon, Virginia 22070-4005, (703) 689-3000, FAX (703) 689-3041 or debbie@cit.org.
</CITE>


