<HEAD>
<TITLE>CIT INDUSTRY SECTORS</TITLE>
</HEAD>

<BODY BACKGROUND="../backgrounds/rib-bk2.gif">

<CENTER>
<H1><IMG SRC="../images/CIT.ribbon.trans.gif"> CIT Industry Sectors</H1>
</CENTER>
<P>
<B>
CIT serves technology-based companies in five key industries.  The industries chosen reflect several priorities.
First, these industries have been identified by the Virginia Chamber of Commerce and the Opportunity Task Force as being key to Virginia's future.
Second, in each of these industries, Virginia has a significant competitive position in relation to other states, especially in terms of expertise within the business community, the universities and the federal laboratories in the state.
Finally, each of these industries has the potential for significant growth as Virginia enters the next century.
</B>
<P>

<CENTER>
<B>
[<A HREF="../industry/infotech.html">Information Technology & Telecommunications</A>]&#160;
[<A HREF="../industry/biotech.html">Biotechnology and Medical</A>]&#160;
<BR>
[<A HREF="../industry/environment.html">Energy and Environmental</A>]&#160;
[<A HREF="../industry/manufacture.html">Electronics and Advanced Manufacturing</A>]&#160;
<BR>
[<A HREF="../industry/transport.html">Aerospace and Transportation</A>]&#160;
</B>
</CENTER>

<P>
<CENTER>
<P>

	<A HREF="../industry/infotech.html"><IMG ALT="Information Technology and Telecommunications" BORDER=0 SRC="../industry/images/itt-icon.gif"></A> 

	<A HREF="../industry/biotech.html"><IMG ALT="Biotechnology and Medical" BORDER=0 SRC="../industry/images/bio-icon.gif"></A>

	<A HREF="../industry/environment.html"><IMG ALT="Energy and Environmental" BORDER=0 SRC="../industry/images/env-icon.gif"></A>

	<A HREF="../industry/manufacture.html"><IMG ALT="Electronics and Advanced Manufacturing" BORDER=0 SRC="../industry/images/elec-icon.gif"></A>

	<A HREF="../industry/transport.html"><IMG ALT="Aerospace and Transportation" BORDER=0 SRC="../industry/images/aer-icon.gif"></A>

<P>
</CENTER>

