<HTML>
<HEAD>
<TITLE>Virginia Technology Resources</TITLE>
<META NAME="description" content="A searchable database of technology-based business, organizations, and resources in Virginia.">
<META NAME="keywords" content="Virginia, business, technology, resources, companies, high-tech">
</HEAD>

<BODY BACKGROUND="../backgrounds/va-mapa3.gif">

<CENTER>
<H1><IMG ALT="Virginia Technology Resources (VTR)" SRC="./images/vtr-graphic3.trans.gif"></H1>
<HR>
</CENTER>
<B>
The Virginia Technology Resources (VTR) list is sponsored by <A HREF="http://www.cit.org/">Virginia's Center for Innovative Technology (CIT)</A> and <A HREF="http://intercom.virginia.edu/">InterCom</A>.  
CIT is committed to technology in the Commonwealth of Virginia; CIT's mission is to enhance the competitiveness of Virginia's high-tech businesses.   
VTR is a partial listing of technology-based businesses, organizations, and resources in the Commonwealth of Virginia.  
You can search the VTR listings for company names and other characteristics, or you can browse through the list alphabetically, by technical sector, or by geographic region.
</B>
<HR>
<CENTER>
<H3><A HREF="http://intercom.virginia.edu/va.technology.mailform.html">ADD YOUR COMPANY</A> <BR>to the Virginia Technology Resource List!</A></H3>
</CENTER>
<HR>


<UL>

<H3><IMG SRC = "../images/blueball.gif"><A HREF="http://intercom.virginia.edu/vtr-search.html">Search the VTR List</A></H3>

<H3><IMG SRC = "../images/blueball.gif">Alphabetical Listings</H3>
