<HEAD>
<TITLE>CIT Industry Sector- Aerospace and Transportation</TITLE>
</HEAD>


<BODY BACKGROUND="../../backgrounds/rib-bk2.gif">

<CENTER>
<H3><IMG SRC="../images/CIT.ribbon.tiny.trans.gif"> CIT Industry Sectors</H3>
<H1>Aerospace and Transportation</H1>
<IMG ALIGN=LEFT VSPACE=0 HSPACE=8 SRC="./images/spacestation.gif">

</CENTER>

<P>
The Aerospace and Transportation Program is focused on developing 
and nurturing Virginia's aerospace and transportation industry 
sectors.  Currently, the major CIT efforts are directed towards: 
<UL>
<LI>  space commercialization;
<LI>  general aviation;
<LI>  intelligent transportation systems; and
<LI>  the infrastructure associated with these activities.
</UL>

<P>
Examples of on-going projects include establishing dual-use launch 
capabilities at the <A HREF="http://naic2.arc.nasa.gov/naic/guide/templates/wallops.html">NASA Wallops Flight Facility</A>, demonstrating 
the effectiveness of new general aviation technology at selected 
airports in Virginia, and supporting industry/university efforts to 
commercialize technologies for intelligent highway systems.

<P>
The Program is working with several organizations in Virginia to 
create economic benefits statewide for Virginia's aerospace and 
transportation industry sectors.

<P>
The CIT Aerospace and Transportation Industry Director is 
<A HREF="../people/jmjerke.html">John M. Jerke</A>.  
For more information regarding this industry, please call him at 
(703) 689-3015 or send an e-mail to 
<A HREF="mailto:john@cit.org">john@cit.org</A>.

<P>
For a list of Virginia companies in this industry sector, take a look
at the <A HREF="http://intercom.virginia.edu/cgi-bin/vtr-tech-query?Aerospace+and+Transportation"><B>Aerospace and Transportation section</B></A> of the <A HREF="../VA.technology.html">Virginia Technology Resources (VTR)</A> list.
<BR CLEAR=LEFT>


&#160;<P>
Other potentially helpful links:
<UL>
<LI><A HREF="http://www.SEVA.net/bus/vabr/">Virginia Aerospace Business Roundtable</A>
<LI><A HREF="http://pratt.vtrc.virginia.edu/">Virginia Transportation Research Council</A>
<LI><A HREF="http://www.bigyellow.com/">BigYellow</A> internet yellow pages
<LI><A HREF="http://www.yahoo.com/Business_and_Economy/Companies/Aerospace/">Yahoo's Aerospace Companies index</A>
<LI><A HREF="http://www.yahoo.com/Business_and_Economy/Transportation/">Yahoo's Transportation index</A>

</UL>

<CENTER>
