<HEAD>
<TITLE>Nitin Pradhan- CIT Assoc. Dir. of Information Technology & Telecommunications</TITLE>
</HEAD>

<BODY BACKGROUND="../backgrounds/rib-bk2.gif">

<CENTER>
<H2>Nitin Pradhan</H2>
<H3>Director of Information Technology and Telecommunications</H3>
</CENTER>

<IMG ALIGN=left VSPACE=15 HSPACE=15 SRC="./images/npradhan.gif">
<P>
<P>
&#160;<BR>
&#160;<BR>
<HR>
<UL>
<B><LI>E-mail:</B> <A HREF="mailto:nitin@cit.org">nitin@cit.org</A>
<P>
<B><LI>Phone:</B> (703) 689-3000
<P>
<B><LI>FAX:</B> (703)  689-3041
<P>
<B><LI>Mail:</B> Suite 600, 2214 Rock Hill Road, Herndon, VA 20170-4200
</UL>
<P>
<HR>
<BR CLEAR=left>
<P>

<P>
As Director of Information Technology and Telecommunications Mr. 
Nitin Pradhan is responsible for  the development and growth  of  this 
sector in Virginia.
<P>
Mr. Pradhan has over 10 years of management experience in various areas of 
Information Technology and Telecommunications including Internet, Electronic 
Commerce, Electronic Document Management, Imaging, Geographical Information 
Systems, Computer Aided Design, and Business Process Re-engineering.
<P>
Mr. Pradhan has worked on several major projects in developed as well as 
developing countries for organizations including Bell Atlantic, United 
States Information Agency and Hewlett Packard/HCL Group.
<P>
Mr. Pradhan received his BS in engineering from Faculty of Technology and 
Engineering and his MBA in marketing from Institute of Management 
Development and Research in India. Mr. Pradhan also holds an MS in 
accounting from American University in Washington, DC.
<P>

